  },
  "Glory": {
    "type": [
      "Physical",
      "Social"
    ],
    "flavor": """
      <p><em>The after-action report was filed, the wounded were patched, and the squad was debriefing. HK416 sat cleaning her rifle with mechanical precision while the others talked.</em></p>
            <p>"That charge across the bridge was insane, 416. You could've been scrapped."</p>
            <p>"But I wasn't."</p>
            <p>"You did it because the commander was watching, didn't you."</p>
            <p><em>416 didn't look up from her rifle. But she didn't deny it either.</em></p>
    """,
    "description": """
      <h3>Effects</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>You find risking your life to be a simple matter, as long as there is a witness to remember your actions. No threat or challenge deters you if you might be remembered for it, making even the most daunting tasks easy ones for which to prepare.</li>
                <li>After performing a check to improve your reputation or gain recognition (such as a check to impress observers with a daring feat or execute a bold tactical maneuver), you remove 3 strife.</li>
            </ul>
