    "flavor": """
      <p><em>The squad was picking through the ruins of a pre-war university when Andoris stopped in front of a crumbling notice board, still pinned with faded flyers.</em></p>
            <p>"Andoris, we're looking for the supply cache, not souvenirs."</p>
            <p>"This building was requisitioned by the Ministry of Defense in 2045. You can tell from the bolt holes where the military signage was mounted." <em>She traced a line of filled-in screw holes along the wall.</em> "But these flyers are from before that. Student organizations. Concert announcements. Someone's lost cat."</p>
            <p>"So?"</p>
